    .col-xs-11.col-xs-offset-1
      .row
        .col-xs-12
          %h3 Values

      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-sm-offset-2
          %p What does your clinic do to make the space welcoming and inclusive for LGBQ-identified patients?
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-sm-offset-2
          %p Answer

      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-sm-offset-2
          %p What does your clinic do to make the space welcoming and inclusive for trans- and genderqueer-identified patients?
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-sm-offset-2
          %p Answer

      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-sm-offset-2
          %p Please describe the ways in which you are involved in LGBTQ community outside of your practice (ex: Do you attend conferences on working with LGBTQ clients? Are you involved in local organizations that serve these communities? etc).
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-sm-offset-2
          %p Answer

      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-sm-offset-2
          %p What else do you want potential patients to know about you or your clinic?
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-sm-offset-2
